Vỗ tay!

14
00:00:45,940 --> 00:00:46,835
[(Giật mình)]
Gì vậy

15
00:00:46,836 --> 00:00:49,504
[Super Manchae thu hút mọi ánh nhìn]

16
00:00:49,505 --> 00:00:51,035
[(Mừng rỡ)]

17
00:00:51,036 --> 00:00:54,365
